sequenceDiagram
    participant CH as Cardholder<br/>Browser or App
    participant MERCH as Merchant<br/>Server
    participant TDS as 3DS Server<br/>Acquirer Side
    participant DS as Directory Server<br/>Visa or Mastercard
    participant ACS as Access Control Server<br/>Issuer Side

    Note over CH,ACS: 3D Secure 2.0 - Risk-Based Authentication

    CH->>MERCH: Enter card details and submit payment
    MERCH->>TDS: Card data plus 130+ data elements<br/>Device info, browser data, transaction history,<br/>shipping address, account age

    TDS->>DS: Authentication Request AReq<br/>with enriched data payload
    DS->>DS: Identify issuer ACS from card range
    DS->>ACS: Forward AReq to issuer

    ACS->>ACS: Risk-Based Authentication engine<br/>Analyze device fingerprint,<br/>transaction patterns, geolocation,<br/>merchant risk, amount

    alt Frictionless Flow - Low Risk Transaction
        ACS-->>DS: Authentication Response ARes<br/>Status: Authenticated silently
        DS-->>TDS: Forward ARes with proof
        TDS-->>MERCH: Authentication successful<br/>ECI 05 for Visa, ECI 02 for MC
        Note over CH,ACS: Liability shifts to Issuer<br/>Cardholder sees no challenge
        MERCH->>MERCH: Proceed to authorization<br/>with authentication proof CAVV
    else Challenge Flow - Higher Risk Transaction
        ACS-->>DS: Authentication Response ARes<br/>Status: Challenge required
        DS-->>TDS: Forward challenge request
        TDS-->>MERCH: Render challenge iframe
        MERCH-->>CH: Display challenge to cardholder
        CH->>ACS: Complete challenge<br/>OTP, biometric, app approval, or push
        ACS->>ACS: Verify challenge response
        ACS-->>DS: Result Request RReq<br/>Challenge result
        DS-->>TDS: Forward result
        TDS-->>MERCH: Authentication result<br/>ECI 05 or 07 depending on outcome
        Note over CH,ACS: Liability shifts to Issuer if authenticated
        MERCH->>MERCH: Proceed to authorization with CAVV
    end

    Note over CH,ACS: After authentication, normal authorization flow proceeds<br/>CAVV included in auth request as proof of 3DS
